[32m[0;37m[32m480H [0;37m[32m133V [0;37m23467383X 12.54% 6610C [32m[Pos:standing][0m[0;37m [0;37mExits:(N)ESW> [0;37mhelp area araton[0m

[32m[0;37m[32m480H [0;37m[32m133V [0;37m23467383X 12.54% 6610C [32m[Pos:standing][0m[0;37m [0;37mExits:(N)ESW> 
ARATON
======

BACKGROUND:

The agriculture-based free city of Araton has had a bad string of events.
First, chance flames ravaged a good deal of their farmland. This would've
been bad by itself, but to make matters worse, strange plant creatures began
attacking the city with no warning from the northeast. The plants overwhelmed
the unsuspecting city at first, until the brave townguard of Araton was able
to push the invaders mostly back and out from the gates. The victory came
with many losses. Most of the people of Araton have fled in fear for their
lives, leaving only a few hardy townsfolk to remain. This was fortunate for
the remaining guards of Araton, as with their reduced number from the
attacks, they wouldn't have been able to protect the entire city anyway.

Glaser, the headguard of Araton has sent messengers to some of the major
cities, asking for assistance from whoever can spare it. He wishes help to
defend the city, and also to perhaps remove the source of the strange plant
creatures.

RECOMMENDED LEVELS:

To aid in the defense of Araton's walls would require an adventurer to be
of mid level (12-15). To explore the source of the strange plant creatures
would require a group of hardier individuals, of higher mid level (15-18),
though to completely liberate Araton from their attackers could require
more.

LOCATION:

Araton is located near the Wendle Woods, a ways northeast of Port Balifor.

CREATED BY:

Ayeka
Added: July 2001
